{"tid":1674564,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"原來是去踩場…… - 高慧然","createTime":"2019-10-25T09:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T09:52:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0fb479ac20349c705b87cd340e9586fb5e0c318d","tid":1674564,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T09:32:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20191025/20793078/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191025%2F20793078%2F&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTd%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=cd9febb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191025%2F20793078%2F&h=e8d2f569\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20191025/20793078/</a><br />\n<br />\n原來是去踩場&hellip;&hellip; - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191025/large/1571901729_ff08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191025%2Flarge%2F1571901729_ff08.jpg&h=45005423&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n路透社(路透社)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在日皇德仁登基典禮大出洋相的柒婆，被日本產經新聞踢爆並無收到外務省正式邀請。<br />\n<br />\n若消息屬實，實在非常有趣。我想起曾經在台灣報紙上看到的一則舊聞：一對貪小便宜的男女混入陌生人家的婚宴，以賓客身份白吃白喝一頓，臨散場還領取一份禮物，打算全身而退。誰知新郎新娘目光如炬，當場踢爆他們並非受邀的賓客。<br />\n<br />\n一般情況下，因為出席的賓客有新郎、新娘的親朋戚友，也有男女雙方娘家的親朋戚友，人多混雜，吃飽喝足了提前離場，不大容易被人踢爆。這一對男女錯在太小家，沒有利是，沒有禮物，逗留時間太長，高調出事。<br />\n<br />\n柒婆一樣，出事的原因是高調。<br />\n<br />\n實在不明白，若無正式邀請，柒婆何必出席日本天皇即位儀式呢？作為香港曠日持久示威活動的始作俑者，她這個人本身已是文明社會公敵，不管她如何低調，都不可能被傳媒忽視。身份本已敏感，行為還令人難以置信地倨傲無禮，在極度重視禮儀及個人自制能力的日本，挑戰國際禮儀之極限，低頭把玩手機。若是有意識引人注目，那麼，她成功了。<br />\n<br />\n作為一個永遠做柒事、不柒不做的失敗政治人物，這一次，柒婆踩場成功，但被落面的並非日本政府，而是她自己。也算是對柒的堅守。 <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk"},{"pid":"30f92442df8cca515180044f1d2d2accc01d150a","tid":1674564,"uid":103870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T09:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />港獨之母"},{"pid":"94ea3675453eca2cfb261f91af422588701cdbbb","tid":1674564,"uid":31200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T09:39:09.000Z","msg":"777冇改錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f959c030b8e35d36039f3b3fa71f9e582ea9c11a","tid":1674564,"uid":201427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T09:40:48.000Z","msg":"而是她自己。也算是對柒的堅守。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce28e734e35574f0ff4550564b8a48e4df4fa652","tid":1674564,"uid":223198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T09:52:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}